Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: archetypes.recurringdate
Version: 0.1
Summary: Field/Widget to support recurring dates.
Home-page: http://dev.plone.org/archetypes/log/MoreFieldsAndWidgets/archetypes.recurringdate
Author: Dorneles Tremea
Author-email: dorneles@tremea.com
License: GPL
Description: Introduction
        ============
        
        This package provides a custom Archetypes field and widget to
        manage recurring dates.
        
        It's currently in a proof-of-concept state to gather feedback
        about a more user-friedly interface for recurring events.
        
        Changelog
        =========
        
        0.1 (2009-11-16)
        -----------------
        
        - Initial release.
        [deo]
        
